can be negative.\n\nRaise RuntimeError if shift is called when deadline is not scheduled"]}, {"name": "async_timeout.Timeout.update", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "deadline", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Set deadline to absolute value.\n\ndeadline argument points on the time in the same clock system\nas loop.time().\n\nIf new deadline is in the past the timeout is raised immediately.\n\nPlease note: it is not POSIX time but a time with\nundefined starting base, e.g. the time of the system power on."]}, {"name": "async_timeout.Timeout._reschedule", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "async_timeout.Timeout._do_enter", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "async_timeout.Timeout._do_exit", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "exc_type", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Type", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "BaseException", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.BaseException", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "async_timeout.Timeout._on_timeout", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type":